examples.en: Maria got up and took a shower in a leisurely way.
After lunch we went for a leisurely stroll.
He sipped leisurely at his drink.
Lucy set off at a leisurely pace back to the hotel.
They had a long, leisurely lounge by the pool.
They strolled along at a leisurely pace.
We walked at a leisurely pace along the shore.
After a leisurely lunch, we went to see a movie.
